reviewText: Awesome service!  Hard to find this video combo out in stores at a reasonable price.  Thanks for a great deal!  Sorry for being a slacker on my review!

Good Double Feature.  Major Payne is one of those movies you can watch over and over again year after year and laugh like the first time.  St. Bilko, while not as good as the original, is still funny.  The two movie combination is a great value for vacations, car trips and an easy pick for the rained out soccer game alternative.

This double-feature was a great buy.  Both of these movies provide silly but real laughs.  Damon Wayans is hilarious as Major Payne and Steve Martin adds his comedic flare as the gambling con-artist Sargent Bilko.  Fun for all ages, especially the "Military Brats.".

Super hilarious!  Steve Martin is excellent in any movie.  Major Payne is funny and touching at times.  Definitely a good purchase.
